The paper discusses automated machine learning (AutoML), which is a subfield of machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI). The paper also touches upon the concept of artificial general intelligence (AGI), which is a subfield of AI. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
